goal: Optimize 50-dimensional Ackley function using IPOPT with warm-starting strategy

decisions.reasoning: IPOPT optimization failed to converge within 100 iterations. The algorithm reached the maximum iteration limit without achieving the desired tolerance. The best objective value found was 1.297e-6, which is close to the global minimum of 0 but not sufficient for our requirements. This suggests that IPOPT needs more iterations or a different configuration to achieve better convergence on this high-dimensional Ackley function.
